16:21.606 --> 16:27.409
115-113 in favour of the winner.

16:27.528 --> 16:29.622
- And still...
- (CHEERING)

16:29.739 --> 16:34.245
...the WBO middleweight
champion of the world,

16:34.368 --> 16:37.372
Matty Burton.

16:37.497 --> 16:40.171
CROWD: Matty! Matty! Matty!

17:19.789 --> 17:20.881
- Hey.
- Hey.

17:27.630 --> 17:28.973
I fucking did it.

17:29.549 --> 17:31.597
(GROANING)

17:31.717 --> 17:32.718
- Ow, ow!
- Sorry.

17:33.386 --> 17:35.184
(SOBBING)

17:35.304 --> 17:36.556
Oh, you did it.

17:40.226 --> 17:41.648
Don't cry, baby.

17:42.728 --> 17:44.025
Don't cry.

17:47.108 --> 17:48.530
It's over.

17:50.236 --> 17:52.113
Do you feel legit now?

17:52.613 --> 17:53.785
- Yeah.
- Yeah?

17:53.906 --> 17:54.998
Good.

18:00.162 --> 18:01.539
What do you want?

18:03.124 --> 18:04.717
