18:07.795 --> 18:09.297
(LAUGHS)

18:09.422 --> 18:11.766
You're champion of the world.
You can have anything.

18:11.882 --> 18:14.055
- And you want a cup of tea?
- Yeah.

18:14.176 --> 18:15.803
A nice sweet cup of tea.

18:18.097 --> 18:19.098
Okay.

18:21.809 --> 18:23.857
Ow! You keep squeezing me.

18:23.978 --> 18:25.730
Sorry, I just wanna touch you.

18:26.522 --> 18:28.149
Oh, God.

18:28.274 --> 18:29.742
Oh.

18:30.943 --> 18:32.820
I'm very fragile.

18:34.864 --> 18:36.332
Look at your face.

18:44.999 --> 18:46.421
(MATTY SIGHS)

19:00.389 --> 19:01.561
(GROANS)

19:23.496 --> 19:25.169
Aargh! Oh, f...

19:26.874 --> 19:27.841
(GROANS)

