(DIALOGUE MUTED)

20:47.496 --> 20:49.624
Okay, okay.

20:55.337 --> 20:57.806
(MUFFLED SHOUTING)

21:00.551 --> 21:02.019
I'm still here.

21:50.142 --> 21:51.314
This one.

22:00.194 --> 22:01.321
It's in.

22:07.243 --> 22:08.244
Right.

22:10.496 --> 22:11.873
- Ready?
- Mm.

22:21.966 --> 22:25.141
- (MATTY SOBS)
- It's okay, baby. It's okay.

22:34.395 --> 22:35.396
Hey.

22:37.439 --> 22:38.566
We're home.

22:41.819 --> 22:43.617
Let's get you inside.

22:50.536 --> 22:51.754
Come on.

23:13.142 --> 23:14.485
You're home.

23:21.233 --> 23:22.826
It's okay. Come on.

23:28.032 --> 23:29.500
Sit you down.

23:35.873 --> 23:37.000
- Yeah?
- Mm.

23:40.419 --> 23:42.137
- Get you a cup of tea?
- Yeah.

24:31.512 --> 24:35.107
I want you to try and point them forward
so they're pointing towards the steps

24:35.224 --> 24:37.272
That's good. I know it's hard work.

24:38.310 --> 24:39.687
Lovely. Well done.

24:41.730 --> 24:43.357
It's a lot to concentrate on.

24:44.984 --> 24:46.202
Forwards again.

24:46.318 --> 24:47.536
What I need to check first

24:47.653 --> 24:51.248
