is you just pop this leg here

24:55.077 --> 24:56.579
up onto the step.

24:58.288 --> 24:59.506
Pointing forwards again.

25:06.213 --> 25:07.965
Do it like we do it at home.

25:09.508 --> 25:11.977
- What?
- Do it like we do it at home.

25:12.094 --> 25:13.971
- Show them.
- Yeah.

25:19.601 --> 25:20.944
Yeah?

25:21.061 --> 25:22.734
PHYSIOTHERAPIST: Well done.

25:22.855 --> 25:25.279
That's lovely. Hand on the banister, though.

25:26.025 --> 25:27.743
Lovely. Well done.

25:28.777 --> 25:31.030
That's it. Got the leg position. Good.

25:31.989 --> 25:33.536
Well done.

25:33.657 --> 25:36.035
- Brilliant.
- Good. Put your hand forward.

26:42.810 --> 26:44.028
(PUNCHBALL SWINGING)

26:49.316 --> 26:50.408
(BALL BEING PUNCHED)

26:58.367 --> 26:59.994
