What are you doing?

27:05.916 --> 27:08.135
- Training.
- What for?

27:10.546 --> 27:11.547
A fight.

27:12.381 --> 27:13.803
Who are you fighting?

27:13.924 --> 27:14.925
Um...

27:16.718 --> 27:17.719
Black man.

27:20.597 --> 27:22.144
- A black man?
- Yeah.

27:25.269 --> 27:27.522
