eh, Matty Burton?

27:28.355 --> 27:29.652
I don't know.

27:31.275 --> 27:32.572
Let's take you upstairs.

27:32.693 --> 27:33.911
- Yeah.
- Come on.

27:34.778 --> 27:35.870
I'll take that.

27:57.467 --> 27:59.686
Um, what's her?

28:01.305 --> 28:02.523
It's Mia.

28:03.182 --> 28:04.149
Oh.

28:07.144 --> 28:09.067
Who her dad is?

28:09.188 --> 28:10.735
You are, Matthew.

28:10.856 --> 28:11.857
Oh.

28:13.275 --> 28:14.618
How long?

28:15.944 --> 28:16.945
Um...

28:18.488 --> 28:20.912
From the moment she was conceived.

28:23.035 --> 28:24.912
Basically, all of her life.

28:26.121 --> 28:28.465
We made her. Do you understand?

28:29.875 --> 28:31.218
No.

28:32.586 --> 28:34.930
Am I gonna have to teach you
about that as well?

28:35.047 --> 28:36.048
What?

28:37.049 --> 28:39.427
That is your little girl.

28:39.551 --> 28:40.393
Oh.

28:42.304 --> 28:43.726
What his name is?

28:44.890 --> 28:46.733
She's called Mia.

28:46.850 --> 28:48.272
- Mia.
- Mia.

28:49.645 --> 28:50.646
Made her.

28:50.771 --> 28:52.444
100%, yes.

28:54.775 --> 28:55.993
I made her.

28:57.736 --> 28:58.783
We did.

28:58.904 --> 29:01.202
- I'm pregnant there.
- Oh?

29:01.323 --> 29:03.291
- Who's that?
- It's Darren from the gym.

29:03.408 --> 29:05.251
He's wrapping your hands before the fight.

